TAGGER
======

Add ID3 tag 'artist' and 'title' on mp3 file using filename.

Usage: tagger [<options>] <filename> ...

Options:
    -a, --album ALBUM                Set album for all files
    -s, --separator STRING           Set separator string for Artist/Title, default " - "
    -v, --version                    Print version
    -h, --help                       Show this help message


EXAMPLE:
tagger 'ACDC - Back in black.mp3'

=> Remove all ID3 tag
=> Add tag artist as 'ACDC'
=> Add tag title as 'Back in black'
(Split the filename with default separator ' - ', see option -s)


REQUIREMENTS:
 * eyeD3 program: http://eyed3.nicfit.net/

